title: Extra Innings: Why the Ballpark?
itunes:author: Derek Valles, Chris Gilson, Denise Baron
description: Contributor(s): Derek Valles, Chris Gilson, Denise Baron | You might be wondering, "Why is this podcast called 'The Ballpark'?" We invited another baseball fan and political economist, Derek Valles, to chat about the overlaps and intersections of baseball and politics.
